                            It would be nice to have all my representatives' information in one place on my phone, kind of like having my Senator's phone number in my Contacts
                        p.quote-source – Emily
                .grid-2-item.pl-xl
                    h3 Interviews with Government Offices
                    p.project-p.
                        To tackle the problem from another angle, I contacted my own reps. I called their offices and conducted surveys on how a citizen could best get their voice heard.
                        It was helpful to understand what happens to a citizen's message.
                    h5.mb-xl Takeaways
