                    h3 Online Research

                    p.project-p.
                        To understand civic engagement on a broader scale, I looked online for previous research that revealed new insights as well as why this problem was worth solving. 
                        Sources included The Annenberg Public Policy Center, Pew Research Center, Congress Management Foundation, The Boston Globe, and GlobalCitizen.org.

